hangmanPsuedoCode

Create an array of possible answers
Pick answer by random
Determine how many letters are in answer
in HTML display a space for each letter in the answers
-if length of answer is 7 letters long, display 7 empty divs

Game starts when a user enters a letter
For as many times as there is an answerLetter
Check  answerLetter against userLetter entered letter in each spot.answerLetter[0] to [answer.length]
Right:
If they are equal, replace empty div with div holding the letter,
Increase win counter by one. && 
If win counter = answer.length display "YOU WIN" & show image, 

else put letter in "graveyard" and count up losses
If 
if wrong answers = 10, display answer = "you lose"
